name: DispatchQueue.AutoreleaseFrequency
desc: Constants indicating the frequency with which a dispatch queue autoreleases objects.

items.name: case inherit
items.desc: The queue inherits its autorelease frequency from its target queue.

items.name: case workItem
items.desc: The queue configures an autorelease pool before the execution of a block, and releases the objects in that pool after the block finishes executing.

items.name: case never
items.desc: The queue does not set up an autorelease pool around executed blocks.

items.name: static func != (DispatchQueue.AutoreleaseFrequency, DispatchQueue.AutoreleaseFrequency) -> Bool
items.desc: Returns a Boolean value indicating whether two values are not equal.
